page.title: 18TELEVISION PROGRAMMES
page.content: There are lots of different TV programmes such as Comedies,Cartoons, Fantasy and Mysteries.There are four main channels BBC 1,BBC 2,ITV and channel 4 and lots of others such as Anglia.There are one and a half hour of childrens programmes from 4.00 pm to 5.30pm.There are lots of types of news,like Newsround for children, 6 o'clock and 5:45 news.There are also chat shows such as Wogan and Harty. Also there are some soap operas like Dynasty,Dallas and East Enders.On Sunday there are lots of Worship programmes.There are also lots of game shows during the week like The Price is Right,Family Fortunes and Connections.On Thursday there is a programme called Top of the Pops which shows the charts.My favourite programme is called Behind the Bike Sheds.
